UISHELL_CC

static final java.lang.String UISHELL_CC
Constant signifying the key with which a customization class will be held as a Session Attribute on ApplSession for the purpose of customizing the UIShell template. The key will be concatenated with an integer to denote the order of the specific customization class being held. Given the CCs UISHELL_CC1 and UISHELL_CC2, UISHELL_CC2 will be the tip CustomizationClass.

See Also:
